This paper deals with wireless backhaul and resource allocation in mobile networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). It also involves optimization of network performance, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions the use of mesh networks, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and system engineering (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the security of the network, which is a topic in cryptography (cs.CR).
